---
/* Main Layout Component
   This component serves as the primary HTML boilerplate for the application.
   It includes essential structural elements and applies a CSS reset and global CSS utility 
   classes that are reused across various components for a consistent design.

   Props:
   - title (string): Sets the page title displayed in the browser tab.
*/

